<h3>Cloudiness and Radiation</h3>
<br><br>
The hot day times and cold nights in the Iberian peninsula (Figure 3 and 4) are reflected in a below-average cloud cover and an above-average radiation in that region (Figure 11 and 12). High radiation/low cloud cover is also found around the Black Sea and eastern Europe. West, central and north Europe saw more clouds and lower than usual radiations amounts.
<br><br>
